casebody.data:
Wednesday, February 5, 1997

MOTION DOCKET

96-1362. State ex rel. Longacre v. Penton Publishing Co.

Cuyahoga App. No. 70455. This cause came on for further consideration upon appellant’s motion for leave to withdraw her motion for reconsideration. Upon consideration thereof,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion for leave to withdraw motion for reconsideration be, and hereby is, granted.
